Math-Vector-Real-Farthest
=========================

Find the two more distant vectors in a set

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Math::Vector::Real
  Math::nSphere
  Sort::Key::Top

The module Sort::Key::Radix is required if the method
find_2d_convex_hull is going to be used.

